@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #2F4F4F
skinparam DefaultTextAlignment center

left to right direction

title C3 - Arquitectura NetworkPolicy S2 (baseline, basic, moderate, strict)

actor "k6 S2 runner" as k6

node "Namespace mubench-real" {
  component "auth-service" as auth
  component "api-service" as api
  component "data-service" as data
  database "postgres" as db
}

cloud "CNI Enforcement\n(Calico/Cilium)" as cni

k6 --> auth : HTTP NodePort 30184 (/login)
k6 --> api : HTTP NodePort 30181 (/profile,/users)
api --> data : HTTP 8080
data --> db : TCP 5432

cni ..> api : aplica reglas Egress
cni ..> data : aplica reglas Ingress/Egress
cni ..> db : aplica reglas Ingress

note right of cni
C3/baseline:
- sin NetworkPolicy (red plana)

C3/basic:
- api -> data permitido
- data -> postgres permitido
- DNS permitido

C3/moderate:
- como basic + egress explicito api-service

C3/strict:
- api-service egress SOLO DNS
- api -> data bloqueado intencionalmente

Nota S2 final:
- El benchmark de C3 se ejecuta via NodePort HTTP
- El control actua en trafico inter-servicio (CNI)
end note

@enduml
